        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Blood Message: NetEase's New AAA Single-Player Project Revealed]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/blood-message-neteases-new-aaa-single-player-project-revealed/1100-6532579/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
            <guid>https://www.resetera.com/threads/blood-message-neteases-new-aaa-single-player-project-revealed.1223778/</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[https://www.gamespot.com/articles/blood-message-neteases-new-aaa-single-player-project-revealed/1100-6532579/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f<br/><br/><div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><p>
    <span data-nosnippet="">GameSpot may receive revenue from affiliate and advertising partnerships for sharing this content and from purchases through links.</span>
  </p><article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6532579">

            
            
  


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>NetEase Game has announced a new game called Blood Message, which it describes as its first "AAA" single-player experience that is under development at Naraka: Bladepoint studio 24 Entertainment. Set during the final years of the Tang Dynasty, the game follows a nameless messenger and his young son as they embark on a 1,000 mile journey to Chang'an, the heart of the Tang Empire.</p><p>Fraught with peril, the trek sees the hero encounter difficult terrain and brutal sieges unfolding in the land. A trailer for the game featuring a mix of gameplay and cinematics has also been released, and you can watch it below.</p><p data-embed-type="video" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n6IwsMWTVGI" data-width="100%" data-height="100%">          <iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/n6IwsMWTVGI" height="100%" width="100%" scrolling="no" frameborder="" webkitallowfullscreen="" mozallowfullscreen="" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p>NetEase says players can expect "cinematic storytelling" and realistic combat that blends stealth and survival mechanics, as well as expansive landscapes inspired by East and Central Asia. At its core, the company says Blood Message is about how ordinary people leave their mark on history as unsung heroes. The story focuses on a father and his son as they navigate a collapsing world and find themselves torn between duty and family.</p><p>"We are ushering players into a new generation of high adventure with Blood Message," NetEase executive VP Zhipeng Hu said in a press statement. "As our first completely single-player focused experience from NetEase Games, after two decades of deep dedication to the gaming industry, we are prepared to deliver a truly epic and cinematic experience for players around the world."</p><h2>Blood Message screens</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518208-bloodmessage_13.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4518208" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1920" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518208-bloodmessage_13.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4518208"></a><figcaption>Blood Message</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518208-bloodmessage_13.jpg"></figure><figure data-embed-type="gallery" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518210-bloodmessage_01.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518211-bloodmessage_02.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518212-bloodmessage_03.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518213-bloodmessage_04.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518214-bloodmessage_05.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518215-bloodmessage_06.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518216-bloodmessage_07.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518217-bloodmessage_08.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518218-bloodmessage_09.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518219-bloodmessage_10.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518220-bloodmessage_11.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518221-bloodmessage_12.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518222-bloodmessage_14.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518223-bloodmessage_15.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518224-bloodmessage_16.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518225-bloodmessage_17.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518226-bloodmessage_18.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4518210,1300-4518211,1300-4518212,1300-4518213,1300-4518214,1300-4518215,1300-4518216,1300-4518217,1300-4518218,1300-4518219,1300-451822