bloodmessage_04.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518214-bloodmessage_05.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518215-bloodmessage_06.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518216-bloodmessage_07.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518217-bloodmessage_08.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518218-bloodmessage_09.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518219-bloodmessage_10.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518220-bloodmessage_11.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518221-bloodmessage_12.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518222-bloodmessage_14.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518223-bloodmessage_15.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518224-bloodmessage_16.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518225-bloodmessage_17.jpg,https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4518226-bloodmessage_18.jpg"></figure><p>Blood Message doesn't have a release date yet, but it will arrive on PC and console in the future. This is one of several upcoming games inspired by Chinese history and folklore that is in development, with other titles like Project: The Perceiver, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/open-world-chinese-rpg-where-winds-meet-gets-beta-soon-heres-how-to-sign-up/1100-6530785/">Where Winds Meet</a>, <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/wuchang-fallen-feathers-might-be-the-next-big-soulslike-to-come-from-china/1100-6527245/">Wuchang: Fallen Feathers</a>, and <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/phantom-blade-zero-dev-compares-the-action-rpgs-level-design-to-dark-souls/1100-6525296/">Phantom Blade Zero</a> also on the way.</p>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
